name: v0.3.0
body:
## What's Changed
* Add CONTRIBUTING.md by @liamcervante in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/13
* [COMPLIANCE] Update MPL-2.0 LICENSE by @hashicorp-copywrite in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/14
* Update to use official provider in examples by @liamcervante in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/15
* [COMPLIANCE] Add Copyright and License Headers by @hashicorp-copywrite in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/16
* Include a file for the human state output when executing equivalence tests by @liamcervante in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/17

## New Contributors
* @hashicorp-copywrite made their first contribution in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/14

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/compare/v0.2.1...v0.3.0

name: v0.2.1
body:
## What's Changed
* Remove the terraform_version field from the prior state by @liamcervante in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/11
* Convert relative binary paths to absolute paths by @liamcervante in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/10
* Add a post submit action that makes sure the examples are up to date by @liamcervante in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/12


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/compare/v0.2.0...v0.2.1

name: v0.2.0
body:
## What's Changed
* Allow individual tests to execute custom command sets by @liamcervante in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/8
* Add additional flag to execute a subset of the available tests. by @liamcervante in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/6
* Introduce support for including non-json files in the equivalence tests. by @liamcervante in https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/pull/7


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-equivalence-testing/compare/v0.1.0...v0.2.0
